metadata.name: DIAMOND
metadata.description:
This is 1 NFT in a collection of 7 videos that have been released as a single unique edition.
The diamond is the king of gemstones, the measure of beauty and the standard of hardness. However, this stone is not as simple and unambiguous as it seems at first glance. It has amazing powers that help its wearer thrive and live an even fuller life.
My video is loaded with prosperity and wealth that will happen in your life!!!

Translated with www.DeepL.com/Translator (free version)
